Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,夢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.73,0:00:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,夢本應是有終點的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.18,0:00:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,無論是多麼幸福的夢…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.55,0:00:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,還是多麼恐怖的夢…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.47,0:00:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,都會在溫暖的被窩中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.62,0:00:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,在媽媽的呼喚聲中結束
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.64,0:00:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,日復一日…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.50,0:00:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我都會迎來不變的清晨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.08,0:00:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,但是現在…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.56,0:00:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,不知從何時開始　夢失去了終點…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.84,0:02:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,快別再哭了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.80,0:02:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你到底是怎麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.32,0:02:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你倒是說話啊　亞由亞由
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.17,0:02:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,嗚咕～　我不是亞由亞由啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.45,0:02:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,啊　原來你會說話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.55,0:02:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,別這麼盯著我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.35,0:02:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,莫非　我長得和你自幼離別的哥哥一模一樣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.04,0:02:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我該回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.31,0:02:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你的肚子餓了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.23,0:02:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,嗚咕…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.90,0:02:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,果然還是肚子餓了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.22,0:02:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.25,0:02:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,好　我買點吃的給你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.42,0:02:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,有什麼想吃的東西嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.47,0:02:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你就沒有什麼喜歡吃的東西嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.89,0:02:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,鯛魚燒…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.32,0:03:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,是鯛魚燒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.76,0:03:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,好　你在這裡等著我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.80,0:03:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.51,0:03:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,假日的奇想曲\N～caprice～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.03,0:03:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了　你沒有走掉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.08,0:03:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你說過要我在這裡等著的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.32,0:03:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,真乖真乖
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.30,0:03:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,給你　我們一起吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.70,0:03:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,熱呼呼的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.65,0:03:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,鯛魚燒要剛出爐的時候才最好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.84,0:03:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,太好吃了　你也嘗嘗看嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.52,0:04:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,是鹹的呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.82,0:04:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,那是剛才眼淚的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.70,0:04:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,但是　真好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.59,0:04:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.49,0:04:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.89,0:04:17.06,DefaultS,,0,0,0,,所以我那時也很緊張呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.48,0:04:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你剛才為什麼要哭呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.65,0:04:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,啊　沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.64,0:04:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,不願意說的話我今天就不再問了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.65,0:04:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我該回家去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.54,0:04:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,再見　亞由亞由
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.68,0:04:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.61,0:04:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是亞由亞由…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.50,0:04:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.25,0:04:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼　我該走了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.10,0:04:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.29,0:04:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣我會走不了的啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.25,0:04:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,鯛魚燒…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.48,0:04:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.37,0:05:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我還想再吃鯛魚燒…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.53,0:05:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你這麼喜歡它嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.70,0:05:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.67,0:05:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,還想再和我一起吃嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.76,0:05:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.67,0:05:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼　明天同一個時間\N\N我會在車站前的木椅那裡等著你的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.41,0:05:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你不會撒謊吧…？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.58,0:05:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不會
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.68,0:05:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我一定會來的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.30,0:05:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,一言為定
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.50,0:05:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯　一言為定
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.47,0:05:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,打勾勾…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.90,0:05:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,用不著打勾勾　我也一定會來的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.82,0:05:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,嗚咕…　打勾勾…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.28,0:05:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.97,0:05:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,一言為定
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.69,0:05:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼　明天再見吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.82,0:05:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.72,0:05:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.47,0:06:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.19,0:06:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯　拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.87,0:06:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,啊…！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.37,0:06:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,大騙子…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.82,0:06:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯…？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.87,0:06:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,3
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.25,0:06:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,2
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.69,0:06:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,1
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.74,0:06:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,0！！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.71,0:06:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.44,0:07:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,啊嗚～　嚇死我了～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.82,0:07:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.45,0:07:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,哎！？　這個嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.28,0:07:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,是跑來報復我　結果又失敗了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.80,0:07:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,才…　才不是呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.87,0:07:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼？　那塊蒟蒻難道是你的宵夜嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.42,0:07:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,這…　這個…？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.32,0:07:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,是…　是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.44,0:07:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,那就吃給我看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.36,0:07:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,哎？　現…　現在就要吃嗎…？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.66,0:07:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是本來就打算要吃的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.89,0:07:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,啊嗚…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.64,0:07:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,好吃嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.74,0:07:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有味道…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.08,0:07:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了？　吃得爽快一點嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.40,0:07:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.03,0:07:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,肚子已經飽了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.92,0:07:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,浪費食物是要遭報應的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.93,0:07:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,啊嗚～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.00,0:07:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.30,0:07:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,真…　真琴正在吃蒟蒻呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.24,0:07:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,據說是她的宵夜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.77,0:07:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,蒟蒻？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.02,0:07:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你餓成這樣了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.23,0:07:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.57,0:07:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我幫你做點吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.10,0:07:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,可是肚子已經不餓了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.62,0:07:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,恭喜你　真琴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.34,0:07:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,啊嗚～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.03,0:08:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的　別妨礙我的睡眠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.03,0:08:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,今天必須把這些整理好才行了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.49,0:08:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.16,0:08:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,早安　真琴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.73,0:08:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,啊嗚～…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.07,0:08:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你清晨的問候語難道是「啊嗚」嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.13,0:08:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,胃一直在痛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.31,0:08:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,誰叫你大半夜的還貪吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.08,0:08:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我才沒貪吃呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.15,0:08:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,那是為了往祐一的臉上…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.35,0:08:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我的臉上怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.45,0:08:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,啊嗚～…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.60,0:08:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,走著瞧吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.56,0:08:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我要出門一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.82,0:08:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,您要去購物嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.22,0:08:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯　另外名雪忘記帶便當了　所以我打算送去給她
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.19,0:09:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,那孩子今天也參加田徑隊的練習去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.82,0:09:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,那就讓我替您去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.30,0:09:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,田徑隊的隊長嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.31,0:09:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,她訓練時會是怎麼的一副模樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.40,0:09:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,名雪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.91,0:09:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,祐一
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.43,0:09:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你幫我送過來了嗎　謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.88,0:09:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,好漂亮的建築啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.96,0:09:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,因為這所學校是很重視社團活動的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.01,0:09:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你很賣力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.04,0:09:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,因為很快就是大賽了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.84,0:10:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我必須回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.52,0:10:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以在這裡觀摩一下嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.88,0:10:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯　站在角落裡的話是沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.95,0:10:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你　祐一
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.25,0:10:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯？　香里？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.02,0:10:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,相澤君
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.66,0:10:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你是來參加社團活動的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.74,0:10:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.87,0:10:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,名雪和你在假日裡也這麼認真啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.19,0:10:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,那只有名雪而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.44,0:10:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是不想待在家裡罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.51,0:10:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,和父母吵架了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.67,0:10:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.36,0:11:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,相澤君　你已經習慣這所學校了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.74,0:11:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然只上過幾天課　但已經習慣一點了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.37,0:11:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,同班裡能有認識的人在　你也方便了很多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.68,0:11:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你是說名雪嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.25,0:11:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,可不能給名雪添太多麻煩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.84,0:11:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,多虧了她　你才能融入到班裡　所以要感謝她才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.84,0:11:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.07,0:11:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,名雪雖然看起來是個樂天派　但有時卻會很勉強自己
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.57,0:11:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你要多多體諒她才行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.28,0:11:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,她每次參加社團活動都會一直練習到氣喘吁吁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.22,0:11:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,原來這就是她愛賴床的原因嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.46,0:11:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我想那大概是天生的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.28,0:11:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我想也是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.53,0:11:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,啊　祐一
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.48,0:11:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,啊…　秋子阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.56,0:11:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起　假日裡還要這麼麻煩你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.00,0:11:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,不　小事一樁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.58,0:12:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,再說　也不能讓秋子阿姨自己搬這麼重的東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.90,0:12:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,能有祐一在　真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.53,0:12:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,祐一君～！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.50,0:12:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,果然是祐一君啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.59,0:12:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我們又見面了呢～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.97,0:12:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.65,0:12:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,嗚咕～　又撞到鼻子了～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.88,0:12:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,這次肯定不是我的錯了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.70,0:12:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.27,0:12:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,啊　嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.17,0:12:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,她是祐一的朋友嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.89,0:12:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,是個素不相識的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.12,0:12:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,哎…？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.73,0:12:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,嗚咕～　太過分了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.65,0:12:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,開玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.77,0:12:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,莫非祐一討厭我不成嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.80,0:12:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,絕對不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.51,0:12:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,今天又吃霸王餐了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.44,0:12:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,才不是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.58,0:12:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,這是剛才賣鯛魚燒的大叔送給我的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.89,0:12:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你都給他添那麼多麻煩了　還真是個和藹的大叔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.93,0:12:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,好活潑的女孩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.25,0:12:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.17,0:12:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,這位是水瀬秋子阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.92,0:13:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,是我借住那一家的家主
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.17,0:13:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,「家主」是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.15,0:13:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,就是家中最有權威的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.27,0:13:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.02,0:13:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,又學到了一點新知識呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.61,0:13:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,祐一　能為我介紹一下嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.40,0:13:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.65,0:13:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,這是月宮亞由　我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.06,0:13:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.09,0:13:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,哎…！？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.85,0:13:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,月宮亞由…？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.24,0:13:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.21,0:13:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,啊　沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.60,0:13:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,一定是我太多心了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.70,0:13:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,祐一君　你接下來打算做些什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.43,0:13:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,正要回家去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.28,0:13:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,今天還必須整理一下搬家的行李才行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.35,0:13:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼　我也去幫忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.99,0:13:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你有時間嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.10,0:13:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯　你昨天也幫我尋找失物了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.07,0:13:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,今天必須報答你才行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.46,0:13:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我們回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.49,0:13:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.77,0:13:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,請進
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.33,0:14:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你裝模作樣的幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.49,0:14:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,還以為你會像平常那樣一頭栽進來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.13,0:14:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我很少會做那種事情…啦…！！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.30,0:14:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,嗚咕～　好痛啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.42,0:14:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.25,0:14:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.18,0:14:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,真琴　快出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.53,0:14:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟你介紹一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.14,0:14:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,真琴？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.35,0:14:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,她是澤渡真琴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.10,0:14:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,和我一樣　是借住在這裡的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.94,0:14:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,別這樣啊　像幽靈似的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.40,0:14:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,下來打個招呼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.26,0:14:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我是月宮亞由　請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.81,0:14:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我…　我是澤渡真琴…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.89,0:14:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,請多指教…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.38,0:14:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你也順便幫我整理一下行李吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.54,0:15:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,哎！？　真琴也要做嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.73,0:15:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你是借住的人　幫點忙也是應該的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.87,0:15:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,啊嗚～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.45,0:15:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,真琴　你沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.56,0:15:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,啊嗚～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.54,0:15:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你可真是一點力氣也沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.26,0:15:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,啊嗚～　用不著你來擔心！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.34,0:15:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,啊　這裡就是祐一君的房間嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.17,0:15:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,累死我了～　已經站不起來了～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.16,0:15:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你才搬了一個箱子而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.88,0:15:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,剩下的箱子交給我　你們幫我把裡面的東西拿出來擺好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.16,0:15:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,對了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.01,0:15:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.28,0:15:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,要吃嗎？　這是鯛魚燒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.54,0:15:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以吃嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.73,0:15:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,多少有些涼了　只要你不介意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.41,0:16:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,好甜…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.51,0:16:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你不喜歡吃甜食嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.98,0:16:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,但是很好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.41,0:16:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,哎　別吃得發福了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.89,0:16:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,真琴呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.28,0:16:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,她說累了　過一會兒再吃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.61,0:16:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,三個人齊心協力　很快就做好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.36,0:16:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你和真琴都只是讓行李越來越亂嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.95,0:16:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,嗚咕～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.34,0:16:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,但是　我們多少幫上了一點忙吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.75,0:17:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯　有你們在我也輕鬆了不少
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.09,0:17:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.76,0:17:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,要是說過要幫忙卻又沒幫上忙的話　我就變成撒謊的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.17,0:17:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,亞由　你找到弄丟的東西了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.77,0:17:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不　還沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.54,0:17:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,弄丟的東西？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.88,0:17:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯　雖然我也不太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.41,0:17:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,但她說自己正在尋找寶貴的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.02,0:17:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,昨天祐一幫過我一起尋找　所以今天我也想答謝他一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.47,0:17:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎　希望你能早日找到它呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.76,0:17:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,給你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.23,0:17:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝您～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.51,0:17:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼我回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.91,0:17:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你一個人能走回去嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.49,0:17:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我又不是小孩子了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.61,0:17:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.55,0:17:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我也想向真琴道別一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.77,0:17:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,她大概在午睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.64,0:17:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,有空閒的時候　就隨時來這裡作客吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.07,0:17:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.09,0:18:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.04,0:18:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,真琴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.96,0:18:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.82,0:18:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,吃不吃蛋糕啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.86,0:18:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,哇～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.45,0:18:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,哦　你回來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.77,0:18:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.93,0:18:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,呐　祐一
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.44,0:18:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,要為我按摩嗎？　多謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.13,0:18:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.22,0:18:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,等我洗完澡再來給我按摩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.87,0:18:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是來給你按摩的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.25,0:19:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我是來拿借給你的筆記的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.61,0:19:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你的筆記…？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.35,0:19:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是借給你了嗎？　因為你說這裡授課進度比以前的學校快
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.39,0:19:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,啊…！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.08,0:19:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,想起來了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.07,0:19:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我把它忘在學校裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.59,0:19:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,哎～？　不行啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.29,0:19:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我必須寫作業才行的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.81,0:19:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.20,0:19:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,明天去了學校後我會還給你的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.20,0:19:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.69,0:19:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,別說晚安啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.78,0:19:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,萬安！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.50,0:19:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,也別說萬安啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.49,0:19:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,那你想叫我怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.16,0:19:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我還想問你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.80,0:19:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我該怎麼辦才好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.86,0:19:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,明天再考慮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.25,0:19:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚早點睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.30,0:19:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,到了明天就來不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.54,0:19:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,祐一要是沒辦法寫作業的話也會為難的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.25,0:19:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我是一個已經超越了這些俗事的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.63,0:19:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我可沒有超越呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.20,0:19:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,那位老師是很嚴厲的　不認真寫作業會挨罵的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.19,0:19:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是說　你想叫我到學校去把筆記拿回來給你吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.81,0:20:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不是這個意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.51,0:20:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧　我到學校去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.02,0:20:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,哎…？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.66,0:20:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,學校大概不會開門的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.36,0:20:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,或許能夠找到可以打開的窗戶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.69,0:20:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,找不到的話就敲碎玻璃闖進去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.76,0:20:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.18,0:20:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,外面很冷的啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.51,0:20:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,沒關係　就當作是活動一下了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.78,0:20:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,真的不要緊嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.50,0:20:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,香里叮囑過我　不可以給你添麻煩的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.32,0:20:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起…　害得你連續去學校兩次
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.13,0:20:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,這是我自作自受　別在意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.60,0:20:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,好多星星啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.76,0:21:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,好了　快點回家去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.40,0:23:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,…我是征討妖魔的使者
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.56,0:23:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,比如可以說「你被退學了！」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.77,0:23:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我才不想玩這個呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.68,0:23:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,征討妖魔的使者征討妖魔的使者征討妖魔的…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.58,0:23:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,秋子阿姨的烹飪手藝真棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.07,0:23:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,有機會的話嘗嘗她的特製果醬吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.88,0:24:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你想吃什麼嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.36,0:24:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,祐一真的像是哥哥一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.52,0:24:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我還以為要沒命了呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.76,0:24:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你來幹什麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.16,0:24:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.96,0:24:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(300,0)}妖魔們的小夜曲\N～serenade～
